This app evaluates scalar and batched FK (blaze backend) with all optimizations turned on for different robots.

* Files in gen/scalar are generated by `samples/scalar_rla_fk.cpp`
* Files in gen/batched are generated by `samples/batched_rla_fk.cpp`
* Files in gen/eigenmatrix are generated by `samples/eigenmatrix_fk.cpp`
* Full generation script is: `helper_scripts/generate_fk.sh`
